house.title: Family House
house.description: Very nice one level home w/ huge Shop! 3 spacious bedrooms with newer carpet, 2 full bath. Layout of home allows for separation with one bed and bath on opposite end of home. Wonderful covered patio great for entertaining and largebackyard. 33x40 shop has plenty of storage along with a14ft RV door, half bath, kitchenette and loft!
